author: striker
msg: * subversion/libsvn_wc/merge.c
(svn_wc_merge):
Setup conflict markers to display in merged output.  Conform
to 'diff3' for now, maybe make it configurable in the future.
Start using our internal diff to do the merging.

author: striker
msg: Revert rev 4603.  Introducing newlines was a bad idea, which
'diff3' doesn't do.

author: striker
msg: Create a branch to work on integration of the internal diff lib.

author: striker
msg: * subversion/libsvn_delta/diff_file.c
(svn_diff3__file_output_line):
Take note if the last output line had a LF or not.
(svn_diff3__file_output_conflict):
Insert a LF prior to the conflict marker, if the previous line
didn't have one.
(svn_diff3_file_output):
Initialize the last_had_lf flag so that conflicts starting on
the first line don't result in an empty first line.

author: mass
msg: Added beginning of server certificate support.
* subversion/libsvn_ra_dav/session.c: added struct ssl_verify_baton_t,
for passing in the appropriate server config group, and passing out
any valid error. ssl_set_verify_callback now performs verification.
The ssl-authorities-file config option points to an CA certificate
collection. Still needs proper error reporting.
